We're thrilled to launch the official MEG blog, your go-to resource for professional audiovisual equipment rental advice in Malaga and the Costa del Sol.

## What You'll Find Here

From acoustic setup guides to lighting design blueprints, our technical team shares hard-won expertise from hundreds of events across Andalucía.

### Topics We Cover

- **Sound Systems**: High-fidelity setups for weddings, conferences, and parties
- **Stage Lighting**: Romantic ambient lighting and professional stage rigs
- **Projection**: Laser projectors and screens for corporate presentations

Stay tuned for weekly technical guides from our team.
